msgid "Vidik & Inteligenca"
msgstr "Aspect & Intelligence"

msgid "Vrh"
msgstr "Top"

msgid "Človeški vmesnik sistema. Podatke iz spodnjih nivojev spremenimo v uporabno informacijo — vizualizacija, nadzor in povezava z višjimi poslovnimi sistemi."
msgstr "The human interface of the system. We turn data from lower levels into useful information — visualization, monitoring and connection to higher business systems."

msgid "Logika & Nadzor"
msgstr "Logic & Control"

msgid "Jedro"
msgstr "Core"

msgid "Možgani avtomatiziranega sistema. Fizični svet postane inteligenten — avtomatika, krmilna logika in medsebojna integracija naprav."
msgstr "The brain of the automated system. The physical world becomes intelligent — automation, control logic and mutual integration of devices."

msgid "Fizika & Energetika"
msgstr "Physics & Energy"

msgid "Osnova"
msgstr "Foundation"

msgid "Trdni temelji brez katerih višji nivoji ne delujejo. Strojna oprema, elektrika, senzorji in aktuatorji — elektrotehniko in strojništvo združimo v celoto."
msgstr "Solid foundations without which the higher levels do not work. Hardware, electricity, sensors and actuators — we bring electrical engineering and mechanical engineering together into a whole."

msgid "Izvedite več"
msgstr "Learn more"
